sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as ChuTaiKhoan
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant UserSvc as UserService
participant Redis as Redis_ProfileCache
participant UserDb as Mongo_UserProfile

Note over User,UserDb: Chặng 1 - Xem hồ sơ và cache
User->>Client: Mở trang hồ sơ
Client->>Gateway: GET /api/users/me
Gateway->>UserSvc: Forward
UserSvc->>Redis: GET user:<userId>
alt Cache hit
  UserSvc-->>Client: Trả hồ sơ từ cache
else Cache miss
  UserSvc->>UserDb: Query profile
  UserSvc->>Redis: SET cache
  UserSvc-->>Client: Trả hồ sơ từ DB
end
